REPORT ZRSA18_10.

Data: gv_a type i,
      gv_b like gv_a,
      gv_r like gv_b.

gv_a = 10.
gv_b = 20.

*Subroutine
PERFORM cal USING gv_a gv_b
            CHANGING gv_r.     "PERFORM : 호출한다,  cal을 호출할때 gv_a도 보내겠다.



WRITE gv_r.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form cal
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM cal USING VALUE(p_a)  "p_a -> gv_a를 받음.(파라미터 변수)
               VALUE(p_b)
         CHANGING VALUE(p_r).  "값까지 돌려줌!
  p_a = 11.
  p_r = p_a + p_b.
ENDFORM.
